tip.text: It wasn't so hard to fall in love with this place. Try everything. Come for brunch. Then dinner!
Daily Provs = Daily Robbery... robbing my cravings out of misery, or robbing me from tasting some of their items because they sell out before 10AM. Liked going in the afternoon with the 2PM crowd
Tagine, Bouillabaisse, Octopus, and Truffle Hummus = ✔️ you know you find a gem in NY when you can't stop returning back for 2nds, 3rds... plus the service is great ❣
